*15.5% [[Asian American|Asian]]
*0.7% [[Native Americans in the United States|Native American]]
*0.1% [[Native Hawaiian]] or [[Pacific Islander American|Pacific Islander]]
*3.4% [[Multiracial American|Two or more races]]

In addition, 19.1%  were [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino]], of any race.&lt;ref name= census2016/&gt;

